As of the [[2020 United States census]], there were 711 people, 323 households, and 175 families residing in the town.<ref>{{Cite web|title=S1101 HOUSEHOLDS AND FAMILIES - 2020: Branford town, Florida|url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Branford+town;+Florida+&tid=ACSST5Y2020.S1101|website=[[United States Census Bureau]]}}</ref>

